msgctxt "824"
msgid "Tachikawa"
msgstr "Tachikawa"

msgctxt "828"
msgid "Saejima"
msgstr "Saejima"

msgctxt "832"
msgid "Talk_Yes"
msgstr "Talk_Yes"

msgctxt "56_Tachikawa"
msgid "I gather you're looking for the underworld's top informant?"
msgstr "¿Supongo que estás buscando al mejor informante del inframundo?"

msgctxt "68_Saejima"
msgid "Sure am."
msgstr "Sí."

msgctxt "80_Tachikawa"
msgid "Well, there are plenty of rumors circulating about him,\r\n"
"yet the man himself is hard to pin down."
msgstr "Bueno, hay muchos rumores circulando sobre él,\r\n"
"sin embargo el hombre es difícil de ubicar."

msgctxt "92_Tachikawa"
msgid "But he does have a number of homeless folks on his payroll.\r\n"
"They collect intel and such."
msgstr "Pero sí tiene varios vagabundos en su nómina.\r\n"
"Recopilan información y tal."

msgctxt "104_Tachikawa"
msgid "I've never met the guy, but I'd sure like to sometime."
msgstr "Nunca lo he conocido, pero me gustaría hacerlo alguna vez."

